ai-mil3.6.11:1.2_0: “When there’s a difference between them, do they make them fail?”
ai-mil3.6.11:1.4_0: For, sir, in that dragon there is nothing left over I do not.”
ai-mil3.6.11:1.5_0: “Great king, there is no things that can be done by a teacher or by a profession, a branch of knowledge, mindfulness, and situational awareness. There is nothing that you should have done to go forth.”
ai-mil3.6.11:4.1_0: The sixth sub-chapter on mindfulness is finished.
